{
  "texts": [
    "For example, Hirosawa et al. [4] pointed out that the bias encoded in human-generated texts will make LLMs generate biased output; Lee et al.",
    "[74] concerned health disparity may result from low readability made by the sophistication of LLM wording; and Johnson et al. [56] noted that LLM algorithms tend to reinforce the health disparity and to prevent LLM algorithms from exacerbating current disparity in health.Another concern that prevents the wide application of LLMs in healthcare is privacy.",
    "When using thirdparty LLMs such as ChatGPT, healthcare organizations face several privacy issues.",
    "Although no privacy breach of LLMs regarding patient information has been reported, attacks for other types of private information targeting ChatGPT have been found [75].",
    "For example, a breach led to the of users' conversations to unauthorized parties [75]."
  ]
}